{
  "page": "The False and the Fair",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>\"<b>The False and the Fair</b>\" is a song.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Partial_Lyrics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Partial Lyrics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Partial_Lyrics\">Partial Lyrics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_False_and_the_Fair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Partial Lyrics\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"font-style:italic;padding-left:1em;display:flow-root;\" class=\"poem\">\n<p>The lord he came a-riding upon a rainy day,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">hey-nonny, hey-nonny, hey-nonny-hey...</span><br />\nThe lady sat a-sewing upon a rainy day,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">hey-nonny, hey-nonny, hey-nonny-hey.</span><br />\n<br />\nHey-nonny, hey-nonny, hey-nonny-hey.<br />\n<br />\nThe lady lay a-kissing, upon a mound of hay,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">hey-nonny, hey-nonny, hey-nonny-hey.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_False_and_the_Fair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_False_and_the_Fair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The song is sung by <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> before Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> attempts to throw her niece, <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>, out the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_Door\" title=\"Moon Door\">Moon Door</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_False_and_the_Fair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_80\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 80\">Chapter 80</a>, Sansa VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214136\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.013 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 241/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8640/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 790/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 360/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1722/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    8.505      1 -total\n 66.89%    5.689      2 Template:Ref\n 64.79%    5.510      1 Template:Lyrics\n 44.66%    3.799      2 Template:Ref/core\n 17.58%    1.495      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5029-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404214136 and revision id 281055\n -->\n",
